flowchart TD
    A[Lecturer creates session] --> B[Generate dynamic QR code]
    B --> C[(Sessions and QR Tokens Store)]
    C --> D[Display QR code to student]
    D --> E[Student scans QR code]
    E --> F{QR code valid?}
    F -->|No| G[Show error message]
    F -->|Yes| H[Capture student GPS location]
    H --> I{Within allowed GPS radius?}
    I -->|No| J[Show too far message]
    I -->|Yes| K[Save attendance record]
    K --> L[(Attendance Database)]
    L --> M[Calculate attendance percentage]
    M --> N[Update attendance history]
    N --> O[Update lecturer dashboard]
    L --> P[Export attendance report]
